    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what does \"small actions\" even matter? it feels like just rearranging deck chairs on the titanic. it's like people are just pretending everything is fine so they don't have to face the fact that it's already over. i'm just tired of the pretense. what's the point of even trying to build anything or plan anything when the foundation is just... gone? it feels like we're all just waiting for the end anyway.",
